headline: El loco del martillo
author: La Seño María
content: Maria Seno, a famous journalist, visits a restaurant during quarantine and describes the scene. She mentions Gary Julio, who discusses an old crime from 2001 involving Climaco, a man who killed someone with a hammer.

headline: Contento por fin de cuarentena
author: Ismael Lazo, Vecino de San Luis
content: Ismael Lazo expresses happiness about the end of quarantine. He criticizes the rescue of a prisoner during the pandemic and questions the government's handling of the situation.
